      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im working on a new fantasy rpg and i want the playable roster to feel really diverse and not just the usual stuff. can u help me come up with 5 unique character archetypes where each one is inspired by a different real-world ethnic or cultural group? i want the gameplay mechanics and stats to reflect those inspirations so they feel authentic to the culture they're based on.",
